des: 104.3 The Fuse is an Alternative music station based in Appleton, WI, and locally programmed by Woodward Radio Group. It serves Green Bay, Appleton, and surrounding communities. The Fuse plays music from the 90s to the 2020s and artists like Coldplay, Twenty One Pilots, Weezer, Paramore, and The Black Keys.
